Internal Overview:
David is an experienced Strategy Director with expertise in brand strategy through to integrated comms planning. His sweet spot lies in BTL & digital channels, with a track record in sponsorship and partnership strategy. He is a heavy-weight strategist yet capable of rolling up his sleeves and getting stuck in.

His agency experience spans both clientside and agency : Ogilvy, Wunderman, Cheil (Samsung) as well as Gyro & Geometry (VMLY&R Commerce)

Recent projects of relevance include audits and qual research for O2 Priority and DIRECTV (US). Past work for Coca-Cola and the Government assessing sponsorship and partnership opportunities. Prior to this, David has developed partnership strategies for Avios, Costa Coffee, NatWest, Nectar, Shell and Barclaycard.

He recently worked on Nestle Pure Life at Publicis Poke in the water category.

His experience spans FMCG, FS, fintech professional service, sport, telco, retail, energy, drinks, FS & NFP.

Your challenges, your aspirations, your journey. Change isn't just on the horizon. It's essential, it's urgent.
